## aggro cron [local]

PHP_PATH='/usr/local/bin/php'
INDEX_PATH='/var/www/public/index.php'

## aggro news
## Featured/stream build every 2 hours
0 */2 * * * $PHP_PATH $INDEX_PATH aggro news

## aggro news/clean
## Clean news featured table every 7 days
0 0 * * 0 $PHP_PATH $INDEX_PATH aggro news/clean

## aggro news/cc
## Clear feed cache files every month (on day 15)
0 0 15 * * $PHP_PATH $INDEX_PATH aggro news/cc

## aggro sweep
## Archive old videos every day (at 2am)
0 2 * * * $PHP_PATH $INDEX_PATH aggro sweep

## aggro twitter
## Tweet new videos every 6 hours
0 */6 * * * $PHP_PATH $INDEX_PATH aggro twitter

## aggro vimeo
## Look for new Vimeo videos every 2 hours
0 */2 * * * $PHP_PATH $INDEX_PATH aggro vimeo

## aggro youtube
## Look for new YouTube videos every 4 hours
0 */4 * * * $PHP_PATH $INDEX_PATH aggro youtube
